<view class="topup-page page-shell">
  <view class="page-orb page-orb--gold"></view>

  <view class="info-card">
    <view class="info-left">
      <view class="info-icon-box">🪙</view>
      <view>
        <text class="info-label">当前摸金币余额</text>
        <view class="info-score-row">
          <text class="info-score">{{mojinBalanceDisplay}}</text>
          <text class="info-score-unit">金币</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="wallet-meta">
      <view class="wallet-meta-item">
        <text class="wallet-meta-label">当前信誉分</text>
        <text class="wallet-meta-value">{{creditDisplay}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="wallet-meta-item">
        <text class="wallet-meta-label">充值汇率</text>
        <text class="wallet-meta-value">1元 = 10摸金币</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <text class="info-desc">充值到账的是摸金币，不会直接增加信誉分。需要提升信誉分时，请前往“摸金币兑换”按固定汇率兑换。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">
      <text class="section-icon">🪙</text>
      选择充值包
    </view>
    <view class="preset-grid">
      <block wx:for="{{presets}}" wx:key="mojin">
        <view class="preset-card {{selectedPreset === index ? 'active' : ''}}" data-index="{{index}}" bindtap="selectPreset">
          <text class="preset-label">{{item.label}}</text>
          <view class="preset-points">
            <text class="preset-value">{{item.mojin}}</text>
            <text class="preset-unit">金币</text>
          </view>
          <text class="preset-price">¥{{item.price}}</text>
          <view class="preset-bonus">{{item.note}}</view>
          <text wx:if="{{item.popular}}" class="preset-badge">常用选择</text>
        </view>
      </block>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">
      <text class="section-icon">💳</text>
      支付方式
    </view>
    <view class="pay-list">
      <view class="pay-item {{paymentMethod === 'wechat' ? 'active' : ''}}" data-method="wechat" bindtap="choosePayment">
        <view class="pay-left">
          <view class="pay-icon wechat">微</view>
          <view class="pay-copy">
            <text class="pay-name">微信支付</text>
            <text class="pay-desc">小程序内直接完成支付</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="pay-radio"></view>
      </view>
      <view class="pay-item disabled" data-method="alipay" bindtap="choosePayment">
        <view class="pay-left">
          <view class="pay-icon alipay">支</view>
          <view class="pay-copy">
            <text class="pay-name">支付宝</text>
            <text class="pay-desc">暂未开通</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <text class="pay-disabled-tag">待开通</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="warning">
    <text class="warning-text">温馨提示：付款后到账的是摸金币余额，可用于后续摸金币兑换或平台内其他金币场景消耗，不会直接增加信誉分。</text>
  </view>

  <button class="pay-btn" bindtap="submitRecharge" loading="{{loading}}">
    {{loading ? '拉起支付中...' : '立即支付 ¥' + presets[selectedPreset].price}}
  </button>
</view>
